\c 26
\s VaIsraeri, vanogona kurwa, vanoverengwa
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika shure kwedenda, kuti Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi nekuna Eriazari mwanakomana waAroni mupristi achiti:
\v 2 Tora uwandu hwose hweungano yose yevana vaIsraeri\x + Eki. 30.12. Num. 1.2. Eki. 38.25,26.\x*, kubva pamwanakomana wemakore makumi maviri zvichikwira, neimba yemadzibaba avo, vose vano\add gona\add* kubudira kuhondo kwaIsraeri\x + 1.3.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino Mozisi naEriazari mupristi vakataura navo pamapani aMoabhu\x + 26.63. 22.1.\x* paJoridhani paJeriko, vachiti:
\v 4 \add Verengai\add* kubva pamwanakomana wemakore makumi maviri zvichikwira\x + 26.2.\x*; Jehovha sezvaakaraira Mozisi nevana vaIsraeri\x + 1.1.\x*, vakabuda kubva panyika yeEgipita.
\p
\v 5 Rubheni, dangwe raIsraeri: Vanakomana vaRubheni: Hanoki, \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaHanoki; kwaParu mhuri yeVaParu;
\v 6 kwaHezironi mhuri yeVaHezironi; kwaKarimi mhuri yeVaKarimi\x + Gen. 46.8,9. Eki. 6.14. 1 Makor. 5.1-4.\x*.
\v 7 Idzi imhuri dzeVaRubheni; nevakaverengwa kwavari vaiva zvuru makumi mana nezvitatu nemazana manomwe nemakumi matatu\x + 1.21.\x*.
\v 8 Nevanakomana vaParu: Eriabhu.
\v 9 Nevanakomana vaEriabhu: Nemueri naDhatani naAbhiramu. Ndivo Dhatani naAbhiramu vaiva vakadanwa veungano\x + 1.16; 16.2.\x*, vakapikisa Mozisi naAroni\x + Map. 60.1.\x* paboka raKora, pavakapikisa Jehovha\x + Map. 60.1.\x*,
\v 10 nyika ndokushamisa muromo wayo, ndokuvamedza pamwe naKora pakafa boka iro\x + 16.32,35.\x*; paya moto pawakaparadza varume mazana maviri nemakumi mashanu, ivo ndokuva chiratidzo\x + 16.38. 1 VaKori. 10.6. 2 Pet. 2.6.\x*.
\v 11 Asi vanakomana vaKora havana kufa\x + Eki. 6.24. 1 Makor.6.22.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Vanakomana vaSimioni nemhuri dzavo\x + Gen. 46.10. Eki. 6.15. 1 Makor. 4.24.\x*: KwaNemueri \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaNemueri; kwaJamini mhuri yeVaJamini; kwaJakini mhuri yeVaJakini;
\v 13 kwaZera mhuri yeVaZera; kwaShauri mhuri yeVaShauri.
\v 14 Idzi imhuri dzeVaSimioni, zvuru makumi maviri nezviviri nemazana maviri\x + 1.23; 25.9,14.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Vanakomana vaGadhi nemhuri dzavo\x + Gen. 46.16.\x*: KwaZefoni \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaZefoni; kwaHagi mhuri yeVaHagi; kwaShuni mhuri yeVaShuni;
\v 16 kwaOzini mhuri yeVaOzini; kwaEri mhuri yeVaEri;
\v 17 kwaArodhi mhuri yeVaArodhi; kwaAreri mhuri yeVaAreri.
\v 18 Idzi imhuri dzevanakomana vaGadhi zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo, zvuru makumi mana nemazana mashanu\x + 1.25.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Vanakomana vaJudha\x + Gen. 38.3-10.46.12. 1 Makor. 2.3-5.\x*: Eri naOnani; Eri naOnani ndokufira munyika yeKenani.
\v 20 Zvino vanakomana vaJudha nemhuri dzavo ndeava: KwaShera \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaShera; kwaPerezi mhuri yeVaPerezi; kwaZera mhuri yeVaZera.
\v 21 Zvino vanakomana vaPerezi vaiva: KwaHezironi \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaHezironi; kwaHamuri mhuri yeVaHamuri.
\v 22 Idzi imhuri dzaJudha zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo, zvuru makumi manomwe nezvitanhatu nemazana mashanu\x + 1.27.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Vanakomana vaIsasikari nemhuri dzavo\x + Gen. 46.13. 1 Makor. 7.1.\x*: KwaTora \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaTora; kwaPuwa mhuri yeVaPuwa;
\v 24 kwaJashubhi mhuri yeVaJashubhi; kwaShimironi mhuri yeVaShimironi.
\v 25 Idzi imhuri dzaIsasikari zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo, zvuru makumi matanhatu nezvina nemazana matatu\x + 1.29.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Vanakomana vaZebhuruni nemhuri dzavo\x + Gen. 46.14.\x*: KwaSeredhi \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaSeredhi; kwaEroni mhuri yeVaEroni; kwaJahareeri mhuri yeVaJahareeri.
\v 27 Idzi imhuri dzeVaZebhuruni zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo, zvuru makumi matanhatu nemazana mashanu\x + 1.31.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Vanakomana vaJosefa\x + Gen. 46.20.Num. 26.37. 1 Makor. 7.14-20.\x* nemhuri dzavo: Manase naEfuremu.
\v 29 Vanakomana vaManase: KwaMakiri \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaMakiri\x + Josh. 17.1,2.\x*. Zvino Makiri wakabereka Giriyadhi; kwaGiriyadhi \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaGiriyadhi.
\v 30 Ava vanakomana vaGiriyadhi: \add Kwa\add*Jezeri \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaJezeri; kwaHereki mhuri yeVaHereki;
\v 31 uye \add kwa\add*Asirieri mhuri yeVaAsirieri; ne\add kwa\add*Shekemu mhuri yeVaShekemu;
\v 32 uye \add kwa\add*Shemidha mhuri yeVaShemidha; ne\add kwa\add*Heferi mhuri yeVaHeferi.
\p
\v 33 Zvino Zerofehadhi mwanakomana waHeferi\x + 27.1. 36.11. Josh. 17.3.\x* waiva asina vanakomana, asi vanasikana; uye mazita evanasikana vaZerofehadhi \add aiva\add* Makira, naNowa, Hogira, Mirika, naTiriza.
\v 34 Idzi imhuri dzaManase; uye vakaverengwa vavo, zvuru makumi mashanu nezviviri nemazana manomwe\x + 1.35.\x*.
\p
\v 35 Ava vanakomana vaEfuremu nemhuri dzavo: KwaShutera \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaShutera; kwaBhekeri mhuri yeVaBhekeri; kwaTahani mhuri yeVaTahani.
\v 36 Uye ava vanakomana vaShutera: KwaErani \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaErani.
\p
\v 37 Idzi imhuri dzevanakomana vaEfuremu zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo, zvuru makumi matatu nezviviri nemazana mashanu\x + 1.33.\x*. Ava vanakomana vaJosefa nemhuri dzavo.
\p
\v 38 Vanakomana vaBhenjamini nemhuri dzavo\x + Gen. 46.21. 1 Makor. 7.6. 8.1-4.\x*: KwaBhera \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaBhera; kwaAshibheri mhuri yeVaAshibheri; kwaAhirami mhuri yeVaAhirami;
\v 39 kwaShefufami mhuri yeVaShufami; kwaHufami mhuri yeVaHufami.
\v 40 Zvino vanakomana vaBhera vaiva Aridhi naNaamani; \add kwaAridhi\add* mhuri yeVaAridhi; kwaNaamani mhuri yeVaNamaani.
\v 41 Ava vanakomana vaBhenjamini nemhuri dzavo; uye vakaverengwa vavo \add vaiva\add* zvuru makumi mana nezvishanu nemazana matanhatu\x + 1.37.\x*.
\p
\v 42 Ava vanakomana vaDhani nemhuri dzavo\x + Gen.46.23.\x*: KwaShuhami \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaShuhami. Idzi imhuri dzaDhani nemhuri dzavo.
\v 43 Mhuri dzose dzevaShuhami zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo \add vaiva\add* zvuru makumi matanhatu nezvina nemazana mana.
\p
\v 44 Vanakomana vaAsheri nemhuri dzavo\x + Gen. 46.17. 1 Makor. 7.30,31.\x*: KwaJimina \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaJimina; kwaIshivhi mhuri yeVaIshivhi; kwaBheria mhuri yeVaBheria.
\v 45 Kuvanakomana vaBheria: KwaHebheri \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaHebheri; kwaMarikieri mhuri yeVaMarikieri.
\v 46 Zvino zita remwanasikana waAsheri \add raiva\add* Sera.
\v 47 Idzi imhuri dzevanakomana vaAsheri zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo, zvuru makumi mashanu nezvitanhatu nemazana mana\x + 1.41.\x*.
\p
\v 48 Vanakomana vaNafutari nemhuri dzavo\x + Gen. 46.24. 1 Makor. 7.13.\x*: KwaJazeeri \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaJazeri; kwaGuni mhuri yeVaGuni;
\v 49 kwaJezeri mhuri yeVaJezeri; kwaShiremi mhuri yeVaShiremi.
\v 50 Idzi imhuri dzaNafutari zvichienderana nemhuri dzavo; nevakaverengwa vavo \add vaiva\add* zvuru makumi mana nezvishanu nemazana mana\x + 1.43.\x*.
\p
\v 51 Ava ndevakaverengwa vevana vaIsraeri: Zvuru mazana matanhatu nechuru chimwe nemazana manomwe nemakumi matatu\x + 1.46.\x*.
\p
\v 52 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 53 Kune ava nyika ichagoverwa kuva nhaka zvichienderana neuwandu hwemazita\x + Josh. 11.23; 14.1.\x*.
\v 54 Kuvazhinji uchapa nhaka yavo yakawedzerwa uye kuvashoma uchapa nhaka yavo shoma; kune umwe neumwe kuchapiwa nhaka yake zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vake.
\v 55 Zvakadaro nyika ichagoverwa nemujenya; zvichienderana nemazita endudzi dzemadzibaba avo vachagara nhaka\x + 33.54. 34.13. Josh. 11.23. 14.2.\x*.
\v 56 Zvichienderana nemujenya nhaka yawo ichatsaurwa pakati pevazhinji nevashoma.
\p
\v 57 Zvino ava \add nde\add*vakaverengwa veVaRevhi nemhuri dzavo\x + Gen. 46.11. Eki. 6.16-19. 1 Makor. 6.1; 6.16-22.\x*: KwaGerishoni \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaGerishoni; kwaKohati mhuri yeVaKohati; kwaMerari mhuri yeVaMerari.
\v 58 Idzi imhuri dzeVaRevhi: Mhuri yeVaRibhini, mhuri yeVaHebhuroni, mhuri yeVaMahiri, mhuri yeVaMushi, mhuri yeVaKora. Kohati ndokubereka Amiramu.
\v 59 Zvino zita remukadzi waAmiramu raiva Jokebhedhi mwanasikana waRevhi\x + Eki. 2.1,2,4. 6.20.\x*, waakaberekera Revhi muEgipita; ndokuberekera Amiramu Aroni naMozisi naMiriami hanzvadzi yavo.
\v 60 Zvino kuna Aroni kwakaberekerwa Nadhabhi, naAbhihu, Eriazari, naItamari\x + 3.2. 1 Makor. 24.1.\x*.
\v 61 Zvino Nadhabhi naAbhihu vakafa pavakapa moto usingazikanwi pamberi paJehovha\x + Rev. 10.1.\x*.
\v 62 Zvino avo vakaverengwa vavo vaiva zvuru makumi maviri nezvitatu, vanhurume vose kubva pane ane mwedzi zvichikwira\x + 3.39.\x*; nokuti havana kuverengwa pakati pevana vaIsraeri\x + 1.49.\x*, nokuti havana kupiwa nhaka pakati pevana vaIsraeri\x + 18.20.\x*.
\p
\v 63 Ava ndevakaverengwa naMozisi naEriazari mupristi, vavakaverenga vana vaIsraeri pamapani aMoabhu, paJoridhani paJeriko\x + 26.3. 22.1.\x*.
\v 64 Asi pakati peava paiva pasina murume kubva kune vakaverengwa naMozisi naAroni mupristi, pavakaverenga vana vaIsraeri murenje reSinai\x + 1.44. Det. 2.14,15.\x*.
\v 65 Nokuti Jehovha waiva ati pamusoro pavo: Zvirokwazvo vachafira murenje\x + 14.28,29. 1 VaKori. 10.5.\x*. Zvino hakuna kusara munhu kwavari kunze kwaKarebhu mwanakomana waJefune, naJoshua mwanakomana waNuni\x + 13.6.\x*.